				<h3>What is Parallella?</h3>
				<p> The Parallella is an open source credit card sized computer developed and manufactured in the USA by Adapteva and launched on Kickstarter in 2012. To date it has shipped to over 10,000 developers and 200 Universities. The computer has 18 CPU cores and at less than 5 Watts is arguably the most efficient computer in the world. </p> 
			</div>
